      ],
      "summary": "Saylani Welfare Trust USA operates as a critical humanitarian relief organization dedicated to serving the underprivileged and handicapped. While the US-based entity is relatively new, it is part of a broader mission that has been <cite id=\"1\">operating since 2022 to improve conditions</cite> for vulnerable populations. The organization is distinguished by its extreme financial efficiency, reporting <cite id=\"2\">total revenue of $1,727,397</cite> in 2023 with a <cite id=\"3\">program expense ratio of 98.8%</cite>. This means that every dollar of revenue was directed toward its core humanitarian missions, which include the <cite id=\"4\">Dastarkhwan free meal program</cite>, medical support, and clean water initiatives. The charity maintains a <cite id=\"5\">90.5/100 overall score from Charity Navigator</cite>, reflecting strong accountability and a commitment to transparency. Its operations are primarily focused on <cite id=\"6\">serving populations in Pakistan</cite>, providing a direct bridge for the North American diaspora and Muslim donors to support high-impact poverty alleviation and emergency relief efforts in the region.",
